[
    {
        "name": "limit_intro",
        "url": "/BRI/course/limit/intro",
        "unit": "Konsep Limit Fungsi",
        "subunit": "Introduksi Limit",
        "time": "5 min",
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Bayangkan seorang pembalap Formula 1 melaju di lintasan. Jika kita menghitung kecepatannya setiap detik, semakin kecil interval waktunya, semakin akurat hasilnya. Tapi bagaimana kalau kita ingin tahu kecepatannya",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " tepat pada satu momen?",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Itulah pertanyaan yang juga dipikirkan Isaac Newton saat ia mengembangkan kalkulus. Dia ingin memahami bagaimana sesuatu berubah ",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "pada satu titik tertentu",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": ", bukan hanya dalam selang waktu. Dan di sinilah konsep "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " lahir sebagai kunci untuk memahami perubahan yang sangat kecil tetapi sangat berarti!"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "formula",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "Ketika \\( x \\) mendekati \\( a \\), nilai \\( f(x) \\) mendekati \\( L \\)"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "justify": "center",
                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} f(x) = L \\]"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "dengan syarat \\( f(x) \\) sedekat mungkin dengan \\( L \\) untuk semua \\( x \\) yang cukup dekat dengan \\( a \\) dari sisi kiri dan kanan"
                    }
                ],
                "props": {
                    "backgroundColor": "#e0f0ff",
                    "border": "1px solid #000",
                    "paddingX": 2,
                    "paddingY": 1
                }
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "/BRI/course/limit/limit.png",
                "alt": "limit_graph",
                "props": { "maxWidth": "80vw" }
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Jadi, apa sebenarnya arti definisi ini? Baiklah, mari kita asumsikan bahwa kita tahu bahwa batas \"dekat\" itu memang ada. ",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "Untuk penyederhanaan, mari kita asumsikan bahwa kita ingin membuat \\(f(x)\\) tidak lebih dari \\(0,001\\) dari \\(L\\)."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "\\[ \\bigg|f(x) - L \\bigg| \\leq 0,001 \\]"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "example",
                "title": "Contoh",
                "instruction": "Perkirakan nilai limit berikut",
                "equation": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 1} \\frac{x^{2}-1}{x-1} \\]",
                "accordion_text": "Pembahasan",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "stack",
                        "direction": "column",
                        "gap": 3,
                        "props": { "mt": 3 },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "direction": "row",
                                "justify": "space-around",
                                "align": "center",
                                "gap": 3,
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kiri:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(0,9) = 1,9 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(0,99) = 1,99 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(0,999) = 1,999 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kanan:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(1,1) = 2,1 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(1,01) = 2,01 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( f(1,001) = 2,001 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Dapat disimpulkan bahwa nilai \\(f(x)\\) mendekati nilai \\(2\\) dari sisi kiri maupun sisi kanan. Maka dari itu:"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 1} \\frac{x^{2}-1}{x-1} = 2 \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center", "color": "kurai_ao.main" }
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "limit_approach",
        "url": "/BRI/course/limit/approach",
        "unit": "Konsep Limit Fungsi",
        "subunit": "Pendekatan Limit",
        "time": "5 min",
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Limit fungsi memiliki 2 pendekatan yang berbeda berdasarkan arahnya: ",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit kiri",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    { "type": "paragraph", "text": " dan " },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit kanan",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    { "type": "paragraph", "text": ". Limit fungsi dapat memiliki sebuah nilai apabila nilai " },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit kiri = limit kanan",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    { "type": "paragraph", "text": ". Namun apabila nilai " },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit kiri ",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "\\( \\neq \\)",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " limit kanan",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    { "type": "paragraph", "text": ", maka limit fungsi tidak ada." }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "formula",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "Diberikan fungsi \\(f(x)\\) jika"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "justify": "center",
                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a^{+}} f(x) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a^{-}} f(x) = L \\]"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "Maka limit fungsi akan ada"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "justify": "center",
                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} f(x) = L \\]"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "math",
                        "text": "Demikian pula, jika sebaliknya"
                    }
                ],
                "props": {
                    "backgroundColor": "#e0f0ff",
                    "border": "1px solid #000",
                    "paddingX": 2,
                    "paddingY": 1
                }
            },
            {
                "type": "stack",
                "gap": 2,
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "text": "Limit Kiri",
                        "props": { "mt": 2 }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "formula",
                        "children": [
                            { "type": "math", "text": "Ketika \\( x \\) mendekati \\( a \\) dari kiri, nilai \\( f(x) \\) mendekati \\( L \\)" },
                            { "type": "math", "justify": "center", "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a^{-}} f(x) = L \\]" },
                            { "type": "math", "text": "Note: Dari kiri artinya untuk setiap nilai \\(x\\) yang lebih kecil dari \\(a\\), namun sangat dekat dengan \\(a\\), tanpa mengubah \\(x\\) menjadi \\(a\\)" }
                        ],
                        "props": { "backgroundColor": "#e0f0ff", "border": "1px solid #000", "paddingX": 2, "paddingY": 1 }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "list",
                        "title": "Cara Mendapatkan",
                        "items": [
                            "\\(x\\) yang lebih kecil dari \\(a\\) dan semakin mendekati \\(a\\)",
                            "Perhatikan apakah nilai \\(f(x)\\) mendekati suatu bilangan tetap"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "stack",
                "gap": 2,
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "text": "Limit Kanan",
                        "props": { "mt": 2 }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "formula",
                        "children": [
                            { "type": "math", "text": "Ketika \\( x \\) mendekati \\( a \\) dari kanan, nilai \\( f(x) \\) mendekati \\( L \\)" },
                            { "type": "math", "justify": "center", "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a^{+}} f(x) = L \\]" },
                            { "type": "math", "text": "Note: Dari kanan artinya untuk setiap nilai \\(x\\) yang lebih besar dari \\(a\\), namun sangat dekat dengan \\(a\\), tanpa mengubah \\(x\\) menjadi \\(a\\)" }
                        ],
                        "props": { "backgroundColor": "#e0f0ff", "border": "1px solid #000", "paddingX": 2, "paddingY": 1 }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "list",
                        "title": "Cara Mendapatkan",
                        "items": [
                            "\\(x\\) yang lebih besar dari \\(a\\) dan semakin mendekati \\(a\\)",
                            "Perhatikan apakah nilai \\(f(x)\\) mendekati suatu bilangan tetap"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "example",
                "title": "Contoh 1",
                "instruction": "Perkirakan nilai limit berikut",
                "equation": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} g(x), \\quad \\text{ dimana } \\quad g(x) = \\begin{cases} \\displaystyle\\frac{x^{2} + 4x - 12}{x^{2} - 2x} & \\text{jika } x \\neq 2 \\\\ 6 & \\text{jika } x = 2 \\end{cases} \\]",
                "accordion_text": "Pembahasan",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "stack",
                        "direction": "column",
                        "gap": 3,
                        "props": { "mt": 3 },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "direction": "row",
                                "justify": "space-around",
                                "align": "center",
                                "gap": 3,
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kiri:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(1,9) = 4,158 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(1,99) = 4,015 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(1,999) = 4,001 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kanan:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(2,1) = 3,857 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(2,01) = 3,985 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( g(2,001) = 3,999 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Dapat disimpulkan bahwa nilai \\(g(x)\\) mendekati nilai \\(4\\) dari sisi kiri maupun sisi kanan. Maka dari itu:"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} g(x) = 4 \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center", "color": "kurai_ao.main" }
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Pada kasus ini, perlu diingat bahwa:"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} g(x) \\neq g(2) \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center", "color": "kurai_ao.main" }
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "example",
                "title": "Contoh 2",
                "instruction": "Perkirakan nilai limit berikut",
                "equation": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 0} I(t), \\quad \\text{ dimana } \\quad I(t) = \\begin{cases} 0 & \\text{jika } t \\leq 0 \\\\ 1 & \\text{jika } t \\gt 0 \\end{cases} \\]",
                "accordion_text": "Pembahasan",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "stack",
                        "direction": "column",
                        "gap": 3,
                        "props": { "mt": 3 },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "direction": "row",
                                "justify": "space-around",
                                "align": "center",
                                "gap": 3,
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kiri:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(-0,1) = 0 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(-0,01) = 0 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(-0,001) = 0 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "stack",
                                        "children": [
                                            { "type":"paragraph", "text": "Pendekatan dari kanan:" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(0,1) = 1 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(0,01) = 1 \\)" },
                                            { "type": "math", "text": "\\( I(0,001) = 1 \\)" }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Dapat disimpulkan bahwa nilai \\(I(t)\\) mendekati nilai yang berbeda dari sisi kiri maupun sisi kanan. Maka dari itu:"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} I(t) \\text{ tidak ada} \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center", "color": "kurai_ao.main" }
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "limit_property",
        "url": "/BRI/course/limit/property",
        "unit": "Konsep Limit Fungsi",
        "subunit": "Sifat Limit",
        "time": "10 min",
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Pada bagian ini, kita benar-benar akan menghitung beberapa ",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "limit tentu",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " menggunakan metode "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "substitusi",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": ". Namun, sebelum kita melakukannya, kita akan memerlukan beberapa "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "sifat limit",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " yang akan membuat hidup kita sedikit lebih mudah."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "stack",
                "children": [
                    { "type": "heading", "text": "Sifat Limit Fungsi" },
                    {
                        "type": "formula",
                        "gap": 1,
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "math",
                                "text": "Asumsikan \\( \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a}f(x) \\) dan \\( \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a}g(x) \\) ada, serta \\( c \\in \\mathbb{R} \\)"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "list",
                                "bullet": "1",
                                "items": [
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} c = c \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} x = a \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} x^{n} = a^{n} \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} [c \\space f(x)] = c\\lim\\limits_{x \\to a}f(x) \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} (f(x) \\pm g(x)) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} f(x) \\pm \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} g(x) \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} (f(x) \\space g(x)) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} f(x) \\space \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} g(x) \\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} \\biggl(\\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}\\biggl) =  \\displaystyle\\frac{\\displaystyle\\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} f(x)}{\\displaystyle\\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} g(x)}, \\quad \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a}g(x) \\neq 0\\]",
                                    "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} [f(x)]^{n} = \\biggl[\\lim\\limits_{x \\to a}f(x)\\biggl]^{n} \\]"
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "paragraph",
                                "text": "Note: ",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": "Sifat limit",
                                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": " ini juga berlaku di "
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": "limit kiri",
                                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": " dan "
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": "limit kanan",
                                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "text": "."
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Beberapa contoh soal berikutnya adalah cara yang akan digunakan selanjutnya secara umum untuk menghitung sebuah limit fungsi, yang dikenal sebagai metode ",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "substitusi",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": " dengan menggunakan berbagai "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "sifat limit",
                        "props": { "fontWeight": 600, "className": "highlight" }
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "text": "."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "example",
                "title": "Contoh 1",
                "instruction": "Hitunglah nilai limit berikut",
                "equation": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (2x^{2}-4x+8) \\]",
                "accordion_text": "Pembahasan",
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "stack",
                        "direction": "column",
                        "gap": 3,
                        "props": { "mt": 3 },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "stack",
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Sifat Limit (5)"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "justify": "center",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (2x^{2}-4x+8) = \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (2x^{2}) - \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (4x) + \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (8) \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Sifat Limit (4)"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "justify": "center",
                                        "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (2x^{2}) - \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (4x) + \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (8) = 2\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (x^{2}) - 4\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (x) + \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (8) \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Sifat Limit (1) (2)"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "justify": "center",
                                        "text": "\\[ 2\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (x^{2}) - 4\\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (x) + \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (8) = 2(2)^{2} - 4(2) + (8) \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center" }
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "text": "Kerjakan hingga mendapatkan sebuah nilai riil"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "type": "math",
                                        "justify": "center",
                                        "text": "\\[ 2(2)^{2} - 4(2) + (8) = 2(4) - 8 + 8 = 8 \\]",
                                        "props": { "fontSize": "1.2em", "textAlign": "center" }
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Sekarang dapat disadari bahwa jika kita telah mendefinisikan:",
                "children": [
                    { "type":"math", "text": "\\[ p(x) = 2x^{2} - 4x + 8 \\]" },
                    { "type":"paragraph", "text": "maka dari contoh tadi:" },
                    { 
                        "type":"math", 
                        "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned} \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} p(x) &= \\lim\\limits_{x \\to 2} (2x^{2} - 4x + 8) \\\\ &= 2(2)^{2} - 4(2) + 8 \\\\ &= 8 \\\\ &= p(2) \\end{aligned} \\]" 
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "stack",
                "children": [
                    { "type": "heading", "text": "Metode Substitusi" },
                    {
                        "type": "formula",
                        "gap": 1,
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "math",
                                "text": "Jika \\(p(x)\\) merupakan fungsi polinomial"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "math",
                                "justify": "center",
                                "text": "\\[ \\lim\\limits_{x \\to a} p(x) = p(a) \\]"
                            }
                        ],
                        "props": {
                            "backgroundColor": "#e0f0ff",
                            "border": "1px solid #000",
                            "paddingX": 2,
                            "paddingY": 1
                        }
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "example",
                "title": "Contoh 2",
                "instruction": "Hitunglah nilai limit berikut",
